Package: GeoAdjust
Type: Package
Title: Accounting for random displacements of true GPS coordinates of data
Version: 0.0.1.0
Author: Umut Altay
Maintainer: The package maintainer <umut.altay@ntnu.no>
Description: The purpose of the package is to account for the random displacements (jittering) of true survey household cluster center coordinates in geostatistical analyses of Demographic and Health Surveys program (DHS) data. The package allows for adjustment for jittering either in the spatial random effect, or in the raster/distance based covariates, or both.
